\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老母煮飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係最好食一定係呀嫲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed887acdc069a34e568219c5272223ef32a6b95","tid":2013753,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d38e5a0f9bb4d26e4de8d9f8c62dbee85ed379b4","tid":2013753,"uid":202194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:42:26.000Z","msg":"呀婆煮既上海麵，唔知點調個湯真係好食到痴線，次次都飲晒啲湯，呀婆走左十幾年後無食過了.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T02:08:44.000Z","msg":"係唔係落豬肉碎整到個湯好清甜咁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45af7b7756989f40df69e914f29795247e23928a","tid":2013753,"uid":281492,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T02:17:59.000Z","msg":"餸就好多都好好味<br />\n最近媽咪病咗入院幾日<br />\n我見佢終於唔霸住個廚房<br />\n就晚晚落足料煲唔同嘅湯<br />\n第二日拎去醫院俾佢飲<br />\n估唔到平時好少自己煲湯都煲得好好飲<br />\n有阿媽嘅9成功力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阿媽話甜到入心呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gUYaRtg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgUYaRtg.png&h=2f9e5926&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fGVsTGF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfGVsTGF.png&h=cdbaa722&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一日只可以飲流質嘢，所以隔咗渣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OiQAh6i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOiQAh6i.jpg&h=2b52b169&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K6QwAS3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK6QwAS3.png&h=c01c5688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後食得固體就俾少少肉同紅蘿蔔俾佢食"},{"pid":"4f1b6ae46c0e7bd267dd906d26fa3a5ee3a2ab2e","tid":2013753,"uid":171942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b428f7a5835c9ae2fdbb79b8056d3f34b12c4ce","tid":2013753,"uid":18479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"558c295cbd670e6a38f642bbe2f89d22573bba23","tid":2013753,"uid":174001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c46cfc14a8ef8dc89baa2cf47d2cc75222aad57","tid":2013753,"uid":18479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:43:50.000Z","msg":"最好食又算不上<br />\n但係呀嫲整既蔥花瘦肉米粉真係念念不忘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:14:20.000Z","msg":"湯米粉？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:30:59.000Z","msg":"佢應該只係 水+瘦肉+蔥花+米粉 煮only 但唔知點解好好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好有肉香"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:24:19.000Z","msg":"我明!!!!! 呢個真係好好食!!!!!"},{"pid":"74ec2354dda7d2ed6298bc9bcabd9464f741af90","tid":2013753,"uid":98291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T07:30:39.000Z","msg":"細個食老母煮薯仔雞翼好好味<br />\n前2年叫佢返...唔同味..."},{"pid":"0b60679513f6d8669c45697af5825837a73b5300","tid":2013753,"uid":307602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T07:37:36.000Z","msg":"金沙骨 決心要學家傳秘方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2209480a7a53998c5588453d7eca2bb4dec5fb50","tid":2013753,"uid":61611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T07:41:03.000Z","msg":"肉餅<br />\n蒸魚 但唔知係咩魚嚟 釘宮定咩"},{"pid":"039adf635e3c6940415f894f7682f2ab4ef97403","tid":2013753,"uid":227106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74ec2354dda7d2ed6298bc9bcabd9464f741af90","tid":2013753,"uid":98291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T07: